  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the association between medical, demographic, socioeconomic, and therapeutic
      differences on compliance with topical glaucoma therapy using the Travalert device.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To determine the association between medical, demographic, socioeconomic, and therapeutic
      differences on compliance with topical glaucoma therapy using the Travalert device. All
      participants will have open angle glaucoma.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
